<HEAD>Jordan Receives Weapons From Iraq</HEAD>
<DATELINE>AMMAN, Jordan (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Iraq has given Jordan weapons and military
equipment won by the Iraqi army in its 8-year-old war with Iran,
King Hussein said Saturday.
   ``It pleases me to join the Jordanian armed forces in their
happiness over receiving weapons and military equipment, as a
brotherly gift, from the brave Iraqi army,'' said the king.
   His remarks were carried by the official Jordan News Agency and
